column5: Happy birthday Bud. Hope it's a great one!!

HAPPY BIRTHDAY RAF!
Happy to ya bud!! Joe
Have a good one!
HAppy birthday Raf! Dang your catching up! LOL, I sleep too much to age!
Happy Belated Raf...
Happy Birthday Raf. Hope you had a great day.
Thanks again everyone.   Enjoyed a nice steak dinner last night courtesy of the girlfriend.
Happy Birthday Raf.   Hope you had a great day.
Heard this somewhere....  Have a great day !!
WOW! Happy Birthday man!  Have a good one!  Gerritt.
happy b day raf!!!!
Happy bday, I saw that you were planning to attend the Christmas swill so I hope to finally meet you (and a lot of other OFNers) then...  Mike

Happy bday!!!!  Do you still get combo Christmas/Bday gifts?  I always felt sorry for kids who had that happen to them.....haha.  Hope you have a great day!
HAPPY BIRTHDAY RAF
Happy Birthday Rif, I mean Raf, Okay Riff Raff.  Cheers.  Joey
Happy Birthday Raf.  Hope its a good one!
My cover's been blown.  Several years on this site and I've been able to keep it from yas.  Thanks a bunch everyone.  Yep, I still get combo bday/xmas gifts but they are usually BIG!
Happy Birthday Raf!  I hope you have a good one!  Whopper

Hope it's a good one and Santa brings you some hard water for January. Happy B-Day!!  Cheers, 1leg

Hats off budday!  HAPPY BIRTHDAY!  May your throne be cushy and your munchies extra savoury.  Hope you can manage a day out on the water.  cheers!

Raf your one of the lucky ones.... try having your birthday on xmas.... it is even worse!!  hope your have a great day!  Gerritt.
All the 'Best' on this day and many,many more...........Chuck andShelley......
